Class NaiveChase

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.forward_chaining.AbstractChase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Chase, Verbosable

    public class NaiveChase
extends AbstractChase
implements Verbosable
    This chase (forward-chaining) algorithm iterates over all rules at each step. It stops if a step does not produce new facts.
